title: Video Nasty 001 (2013) (digital) (Minutemen-InnerDemons) cbr
description:
1983. Murder most insidious has struck a sleepy rural town in the heart of England and Detective David Gorely is feeling the pressure, not only to solve the case before the killer strikes again, but also from his superiors intent on blaming the corruption of the culprit on the recent influx of horror home videos.

Horror comic set in 1983 England during the Video Nasty scandal. A fictional story that highlights the real world problem of censorship and media control.
